            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-blue-600">Audi A4</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mb-2">Premium ride with refined interior, 2.0L engine, 201hp.</p>
            <p class="text-sm font-semibold mb-2">Price: $65/day</p>
            <button onclick="openModal('Audi A4', '2.0L Turbo, 201hp', '24 MPG city / 31 MPG highway', 65, '@Url.Content("~/carsphoto/audi.png")')" class="bg-blue-600 text-white px-4 py-2 rounded hover:bg-blue-700">Rent</button>
